        "subject": "LU-2806 build: Enable download of OFED release candidates",
        "message": "LU-2806 build: Enable download of OFED release candidates\n\nlbuild doesn't allow download of OFED release candidates.\nRHEL/CentOS 6.3 OFED support is available for OFED version 3.5-rc{1,2,3,4,5,6}\nonly. To test software builds and functional testing using infiniband as\ninterconnect the change enables the download of version 3.5-rc{1,2,3,4,5,6}.\nNote: This change will never land in any branch. It will be removed as\nsoon as a stable version of OFED-3.5 (or later) has been released.\n\nSigned-off-by: frank <Frank.Heckes@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ia5f00f38bbdb3518fd295086caf29f3c1996ce9e\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
